# agentic-engineering-max ships LF line endings on every platform.
#
# Dev_006's repo-level core.autocrlf=true rewrites text files to CRLF on
# Windows checkout. That broke the byte-for-byte migration-parity criterion
# (T-013/T-014/T-016: sources under ~/.claude are LF-only, but the checked-
# out plugin copies became CRLF) and would ship CRLF in a cross-platform
# public release. eol=lf pins both the stored blob and the checkout to LF.
#
# This file is at plugin/ so it (a) governs the dev mirror's plugin tree and
# (b) becomes the public repo's root .gitattributes after the Pattern-A
# `git subtree split --prefix=plugin/` release. See
# planning/state-surface-discipline/plan-ledger.md 2026-05-20 entry.

* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets must never be EOL-converted.
*.png binary
*.gif binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.ico binary
*.zip binary
